name: Kaguya Hime
description: A long time ago, an old bamboo cutter saw that one of the logs he’d gathered was glittering in a strange way as if it was illuminated by the moon... Then he realized that inside was a beautiful and tiny little girl. He took her home because he’d never had children, and between him and his wife, they took care of her as if she were their own daughter. Later, the girl will give them lots of miracles and made them rich in a short time...
